metadata.name: Nirmala Chakra
metadata.description:
An illustration of Nirmala Chakra. An honest and purest girl that have been living her adventurous life alone. The only company she have is her guardian tiger. The tiger was given by his brother in order to protect her.

Name: Nirmala Chakra  
Age: 21  
History:  
She was a former princess in Alam Chakra. A tragedy had happen and she was left alone with a tiger. Now she was in the journey to survive and finding her family.
